public class RndPanel
extends com.google.gwt.user.client.ui.Composite

Widget which renders a rounded panel. This is here because IE doesn't support rounded borders in css, so it is needed to wrap the container with additional html elements. For other browsers this class just produces a class-named FlowPanel.
